{"tid":1211012,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人唔好放棄，入黎睇睇條片","createTime":"2019-06-12T14:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T17:08:34.000Z","uid":5737,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a3e3750ff863b05b3f09a8480f5723fe88bdb780","tid":1211012,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:54:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YCIcwuxHks4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYCIcwuxHks4&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvwg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=cae3b3fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YCIcwuxHks4</a><br />\n50分鐘開始睇<br />\n轉載<br />\n請睇哂條片香港人都可以變成光，唔好放棄<br />\n條片都講得好岩，呢家每個90，00後都覺得可以贏，<br />\n所以依家唔可以放棄希望，無理由咩都唔做就結束<br />\n我地香港無超人，但人人都可以做光變成超人打敗怪獸<br />\n超人可能你覺得只係細路野，但入面同呢加情況完全一樣，唔好放棄希望<br />\n請分享<br />\n分享比失去希望既人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e4167717b4ff4558d86b26f73688fad8a33fe2","tid":1211012,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a5cdb88c50236386ab787f7022d26c5fd5af31c","tid":1211012,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:55:58.000Z","msg":"香港人唔好放棄"},{"pid":"a038f415f0ff75deae666d48d66c907c2a1c1afc","tid":1211012,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:56:27.000Z","msg":"變成光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12934bea9101f3469d314291ff6a6fc00b8b065b","tid":1211012,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:57:28.000Z","msg":"請睇條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\